data.description: Stunning custom home in the heart of downtown Houston medical center area! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom gem boasts a 2 car garage, electronic gate, and an inviting outdoor kitchen on the back patio. The open floor plan seamlessly integrates a stylish luxury kitchen with farm house stainless steel appliances, complemented by an impressive breakfast bar. Enjoy the built in sound system throughout the entire home, coupled with a state of the art security sytem. Pamper yourself in the luxurious bathrooms featuring a jetted tub and seperate shower. Smart features like electronic blinds make this home a tech savy haven! Don't miss out on the epitome of urban living!
